<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h1>Revealers</h1>
    <p>Revealers are triggers that reveal hidden content. To use, we must wrap the trigger inside a container with a class of <code>.Revealer-header</code> and the trigger itself requires <code>data-trigger="revealer"</code> and <code>data-revealerid="something"</code></p>

    <p>The revealer shelf must be contained in a wrapper with a class of<code>Revealer-shelf"</code> and a <code>data-shelfid</code> that matches the <code>data-revealerid</code> from the revealer trigger. Within this wrapper we contain the revealed content inside a div with a class of <code>.shelf-inner</code></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-4">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <section class="Box">
      <div class="Revealer-header">
        <p class="u-floatLeft">Here is some copy and an action:</p>
        <a class="Button Button--icon Button--blue Icon--arrowDown u-floatRight" data-trigger="revealer" data-revealerid="revealerB"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="Revealer-shelf" data-shelfid="revealerB">
        <div class="shelf-inner u-mt-4">
          <p class="u-mb-3">Now fill out this form</p>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="small-9 columns">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Here is an input">
            </div>
            <div class="small-3 columns">
              <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="Button Button--green Button--fullWidth">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

